<h4><b>Problem solving through design</b></h4>
<h5>Personas</h5>
<p>Before moving on the ideation phase to develop a solution, I created audience personas based on my research. This allowed me to identify common behaviours, goals, expectations and problems. This ultimately informs me who I will be designing for.</p>
